Privacy policy
This privacy policy will help you understand how Bookmark uses and
protects the data you provide to us when you use Bookmark.
We reserve the right to change this policy at any given time, of which you will be promptly
updated. If you want to make sure that you are up to date with the latest changes, we advise
you to frequently visit this page.

What User Data We Collect
When using Bookmark, we may collect the following data:

° Your guild's name.
° Your guild's id.
° Your Discord username.
° The reactions you add to messages on Discord.

Why We Collect Your Data
We are collecting your data for several reasons:
    ° To provide per guild functionality.
    ° To log specific events. This to help when any problems arises
    What we log:
        - Guild joins.
        - Reactions on messages. This includes guild id, discord username, what emote, stored emote.
        - To who a bookmark is sent. This includes a discord username.
        - Missing setups. This includes a guild id

Safeguarding and Securing the Data
Bookmark is committed to securing your data and keeping it confidential. Bookmark has done all in its
power to prevent data theft, unauthorized access, and disclosure by implementing the latest
technologies and software, which help us safeguard all the information we collect online.     

Removal of data
When asking for a removal of your data we request the following information:
° guild id
° Proof of ownership of the given guild.
Asking for removal of data can be requested trough Discord. DM the bot owner skeleton man#3276
